node.title: One dead, others injured in crash south of Taup≈ç
node.description: The two car crash near Motutere, on the south side of Lake Taupo, happened about 7.15pm on Christmas Eve.
node.content:
["One person has died in a two-car crash which has injured six people south of Taupō.", "", "
File image. Photo: RNZ / Nate McKinnon
", "The crash near Motutere, on the south side of Lake Taupo, happened about 7.15pm on Christmas Eve.", "One person is in a serious condition and two are moderately hurt.", "Another two have minor injuries.", "A section of State Highway 1 is closed.", "Waka Kotahi said there was a detour in place but motorists should expect delays."]
